channel.title: Bought my new computer :)
channel.description:
So I just ordered my new computer off of Newegg..Really hope none of it is DOA, that would really suck and piss me off lol. It was around $700, not exactly the best, but pretty good if you ask me. Here's what I got
Case: Sentey Burton Extreme Edition Full Tower ATX http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16811322018&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
Motherboard: Gigabyte GA-990 FXA, AM3+, USB 3.0, SATA 6.0Gb/s http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16813128514&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
CPU: AMD FX-4100 Zambezi 3.6GHz Socket AM3+ Quad-Core http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16819103996&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
RAM: G-Skill Ripjaw Series, 2x2GB DDR3 1600 http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16820231277&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
HD: Refurb WD 1TB 6.0Gb/s 32MB Cache 7200RPM http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16822236183&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
Graphics: EVGA GeForce GTX 550 Ti 1GB http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16814130625&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
PSU: Rosewill 600W http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16817182032&nm_mc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel&cm_mmc=TEMC-RMA-Approvel-_-Content-_-text-_-
Gonna buy a monitor next paycheck, Hope to buy some more RAM soon maybe, 4GB should be good for a while now though lol
A few things I'm going to try and get soon..
Monitor: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16824236174
Aftermarket CPU Cooler: http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16835186134
Hopefully it will all be here by this weekend, I'm growing impatient :P
